dream.team.assemble.topology

Class LinkWithWeight

  • java.lang.Object
    • dream.team.assemble.topology.LinkWithWeight

  • public class LinkWithWeight
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a wrapper class for the Link class. It adds a weight to each link, as well as a direction given by the initial startNode.
    See Also:
